\begin_inset Formula $[x(1-2\phi),x(1+2\phi)$
\end_inset

].
 Therefore, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h_{t}(x)\le\frac{1}{2}h_{t-1}(x(1-2\phi))+\frac{1}{2}h_{t-1}(x(1+2\phi)).
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

