\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "lem:avg-local-conductance"

\end_inset

 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

 be a convex body containing a unit ball.
 For the ball walk with 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

 step size, let 
\begin_inset Formula $K_{\delta}=\left\{ u\in K:\:\ell(u)\ge\frac{3}{4}\right\} $
\end_inset

.
